FlowTestResult.name: FlowTestResult
FlowTestResult.description: Represents the results for a flow test associated with a flow version.

FlowDefinitionViewId.description: The ID of the flow definition associated with the flow test result.

FlowTestViewId.description: The ID of the flow test associated with the flow test result.

FlowVersionNumber.description: The version number for the flow.

FlowVersionViewId.description: The ID of the flow version associated with the flow test result.

Name.description: The name of the flow test result.

OwnerId.description: The ID of the user who owns this test result.

TestEndDateTime.description: The date and time when the flow test ended.

TestStartDateTime.description: The date and time when the flow test started.
